HEADWORD: Hyperion
<hw>Hy*pe"ri*on</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr. Gr.
<?/.]</ety> <fld>(Class Myth.)</fld> <def>The god of the sun; in the
